Since 1974, Feather Sound Country Club has been one of the most premier private clubs offering first-class amenities and membership opportunities to fit your family's lifestyle.

Drop Down Navigation Home About The Club Our Team Careers Contact Us Membership Golf Our Course Amenities Dining Tennis Instruction Tennis Shop Tournaments Weddings & Special Events Weddings Special Events Testimonials Menu Home About The Club Our Team Careers Contact Us Membership Golf Our Course Amenities Dining Tennis Instruction Tennis Shop Tournaments Weddings & Special Events Weddings Special Events Testimonials HTML Generator Wedding & Special Events Weddings & Special Events Events at Feather Sound Country Club are our specialty! The picturesque venue will accommodate up to 250 guests for private events and you don't have to be a member of our private country club to host with us. With multiple indoor and outdoor spaces to choose from your Corporate or Social event will be perfectly placed and executed. Let us be the location of your wedding, anniversary party, birthday party, reunion, Bar or Bat Mitzvah, bridal shower, baby shower, continuing education course, client reception, seminar, or any type of event you're planning. If you're planning a wedding, the wedding day you've always dreamed of will be perfectly detailed at Feather Sound Country Club. Your romantic union will be forever remembered as you are surrounded and inspired by nature, plush landscaping, and sunset water views, at the elegant Clearwater, Florida country club. Let the professionals on the event staff, take the stress out of planning your perfect day. Welcome home, the home of your fairy tale forever! For more information call 727-498-0005 to speak with our Event Director. Follow Us on Instagram
